In this project we use HC-05 module for communication with robot over Bluetooth.
The module is quite cheap and well-described on the Internet.

------------INFO------------------------------------------------------------

Supply Voltage:		3.3V (connect to pin 3.3) or 5V (connect to pin 5.0)
Operating Voltage:	3.3V
Range: 			10m
Communication:		UART (via RX and TX) @ 3.3V Logic
Default password:	1234
Dimensions:		37 x 17 mm

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
